auty%20and%20divinity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(former%20Twitter)%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20were%20to%20ask%20me%20-%20if%20there%20is%20one%20place%20you%20must%20visit%20in%20Uttarakhand%20which%20place%20would%20it%20be%2C%20I%20would%20say%20you%20must%20visit%20Parvati%20Kund%20and%20Jageshwar%20Temples%20in%20the%20Kumaon%20region%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20natural%20beauty%20and%20divinity%20will%20leave%20you%20spellbound.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20Uttarakhand%20has%20many%20well-known%20places%20worth%20visiting%20and%20I%20have%20also%20visited%20the%20state%20very%20often.%20This%20includes%20the%20sacred%20places%20of%20Kedarnath%20and%20Badrinath%2C%20which%20are%20the%20most%20memorable%20experiences.%20But%2C%20to%20return%20to%20Parvati%20Kund%20and%20Jageshwar%20Temples%20after%20many%20years%20has%20been%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIf%20someone%20were%20to%20ask%20me-%20if%20there%20is%20one%20place%20you%20must%20visit%20in%20Uttarakhand%20which%20place%20would%20it%20be%2C%20I%20would%20say%20you%20must%20visit%20Parvati%20Kund%20and%20Jageshwar%20Temples%20in%20the%20Kumaon%20region%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20natural%20beauty%20and%20divinity%20will%20leave%20you%20spellbound.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Of%20course%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9FoOsiPtDQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9FoOsiPtDQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1713044060448112767%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EParvati%20Kund%20in%20Pithoragarh%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20revered%20shrines.%20At%20an%20elevation%20of%20about%205%2C338%20feet%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20site%20draw