andrayaan-3%20mission%20and%20general%20knowledge%20about%20space%20exploration.%20Each%20question%20has%20four%20options%20and%20students%20need%20to%20select%20the%20correct%20one.%20A%20participant%20will%20be%20given%2010%20questions%20to%20get%20answered%20in%20300%20seconds.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20The%20best%20performer%20in%20the%20quiz%20competition%20will%20be%20awarded%20a%20cash%20prize%20of%20Rs%201%2C00%2C000.%20The%20second-best%20performer%20will%20be%20rewarded%20with%20Rs%2075%2C000%2C%20the%20third%20will%20get%20Rs%2050%2C000.%20%C2%A0The%20next%20hundred%20best%20performers%20will%20be%20awarded%20consolation%20prizes%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20while%20the%20other%20two%20hundred%20best%20performers%20will%20be%20get%20consolation%20prizes%20of%20Rs%201%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20the%20ISRO%20scientists%20on%20August%2026%2C%202023%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20asked%20the%20students%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20quiz%20that%20was%20scheduled%20to%20start%20from%20September%201.%20The%20quiz%20will%20help%20students%20to%20explore%20about%20the%20country's%20lunar%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20has%20asked%20the%20Higher%20Educational%20Institutions%20(HEIs)%20to%20publish%20the%20information%20about%20the%20extension%20of%20date%20of%20quiz%20to%20the%20students%20on%20the%20platform%20quiz%20URL.%20The%20institutions%20are%20also%20requested%20to%20prepare%20the%20list%20of%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20Maha%20Quiz%20and%20share%20it%20on%20the%20UGC%20UAMP%20Portal.%20The%20institutions%20are%20further%20requested%20to%20organise%20a%20mega%20participation%20event%20on%20October%2020%2C%202023%20to%20ensure%20all%20students%20participate%20in%20the%20Chandrayaan-%203%20Maha%20Quiz.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20quiz%20has%20been%20launched%20to%20commemorate%20the%20successful%20launch%20of%20India's%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20on%20August%202