0a%20grove%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20Santiniketan%2C%20herself%20like%20a%20willowy%20tree.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12104616%2FScreenshot-2023-10-12-at-10.45.0.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221052%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12104616%2FScreenshot-2023-10-12-at-10.45.0.png%201052w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12104616%2FScreenshot-2023-10-12-at-10.45.0-300x296.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12104616%2FScreenshot-2023-10-12-at-10.45.0-1024x1010.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679631%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221038%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOne%20can%20be%20forgiven%20for%20thinking%20that%20the%20semal%20tree%20(right)%20is%20also%20a%20sculpture%20meant%20to%20be%20placed%20close%20to%20Ramkinkar%20Baij%E2%80%99s%20outdoor%20sculpture%20Sujata%20in%20Santiniketan%20(left).%20Photos%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fcommons.wikimedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFile%3ASujata_-_1935_CE_-_Ramkinkar_Baij_-_Santiniketan_2014-06-29_5354.JPG%2C%20Chitra%20Padmanabhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20experienced%20the%20tug%20of%20a%20creative%20instinct%20birthed%20by%20the%20elemental%20relationship%20between%20nature%20and%20humans%20on%20an%20earlier%20occasion%2C%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago.%20In%2012%20hours%2C%20courtesy%20a%20train%20and%20cab%20journey%2C%20I%20had%20travelled%20back%20in%20time%20to%20about%2010%2C000%20years%20ago%3A%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Bhopal%20and%2040%20odd%20kms%20onward%20to%20a%20world%20heritage%20site%20with%20a%20name%20like%20an%20incantation%20%E2%80%93%20Bhimbetka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20people%20irresistibly%20attracted%20to%20%E2%80%98beginnings%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20more%20dramatic%20than%20Bhimbetka%E2%80%99s%20massive%20sandstone%20rocks%20emerging%20from%20the%20warm%20clasp%20of%20the%20central%20Indian%20forest%20in%20the%20Vindhyan%20range.%20A%20terrain%20blessed%20with%20vegetation%2C%20water%20and%20animal%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20on%20these%20natural%20rock%20shelter%20surfaces%20that%20our%20ancestors%20inscribed%20themselves%20into%20the%20evolutionary%20timeline%20by%20painting%20their%20hunting%20and%20gathering%20lives%20with%20immediacy%20and%20spell-binding%20directness.%C2%A0%C2%A0They%20painted%20a%20landscape%20abounding%20with%20wild%20boar%2C%20neelgai%2C%20monkeys%2C%20elephants%2C%20peacocks%2C%20and%20tigers%3B%20bison%C2%A0and%20bulls%20caught%20in%20motion%3B%20hunting%20scenes%20and%20the%20heat%20of%20battle%3B%20communal%20dance%20and%20convivial%20moments.%20These%20images%20heralded%20the%20early%20cultures%20of%20hunting%20and%20food%20gathering%20humans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20journey%20to%20Bhimbetka%20was%20like%20reading%20a%20script%20backwards.%20From%20the%20vantage%20point%20of%20the%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Est%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0century%2C%20one%20was%20bound%20for%20a%20site%20that%20was%20pre-historic%20and%20non-denominational%2C%20bearing%20the%20imprint%20of%20humankind%E2%80%99s%20beginnings.%20A%20time%20before%20script%2C%20before%20religion%2C%20but%20with%20the%20powerful%2C%20invocatory%20art%20of%20drawing%20that%20had%20the%20power%20to%20bring%20a%20world%20into%20being.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20final%20stretch%20of%20our%20cab%20ride%20%E2%80%93%20I%20was%20travelling%20with%20my%20shutterbug%20niece%2C%20Kavita%20%E2%80%93%20we%20had%20our%20first%20glimpse%20of%20the%20sandstone%20rocks.%20From%20a%20distance%2C%20in%20silhouette%2C%20they%20looked%20like%20a%20procession%20of%20Jurassic%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebehemoths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20moment%20we%20set%20foot%20on%20the%20lush%20pathway%20leading%20to%20the%20rock%20shelters%2C%20we%20were%20enveloped%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20sense%20of%20timelessness.%20A%20deep%20silence%20hung%20over%20the%20place.%20In%20the%20crisp%20sunlight%20each%20verdant%20leaf%20stood%20out%20sharply%20as%20if%20backlit.%20Strangely%2C%20we%20felt%20our%20vision%20becoming%20sharper%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20gigantic%20rocks%20seemed%20like%20works%20of%20art%20themselves%2C%20having%20been%20sculpted%20in%20time%20by%20sweeping%20winds.%20Some%20looked%20like%20natural%20fortifications%2C%20others%20like%20denizens%20of%20the%20animal%20world%20%E2%80%93%20giant%20turtle%2C%20lion%2C%20frog%20poised%20for%20a%20leap%2C%20and%20a%20beak-nosed%20bird.%20It%20was%20not%20difficult%20to%20imagine%20stories%20of%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20universe%20being%20inspired%20by%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeeing%20the%20patterns%20created%20by%20perforations%20in%20leaves%2C%20peeling%20bark%2C%20and%20weathering%20marks%20on%20sandstone%20surfaces%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20imagine%20our%20ancestors%20wanting%20to%20paint%20their%20faces%20and%20bodies%20similarly%2C%20their%C2%A0search%20for%20colours%20leading%20them%2C%20but%20naturally%2C%20to%20the%20plants%20and%20rocks.%20The%20purpose%3A%20to%20be%20one%20with%20the%20environment%2C%20for%20camouflage%2C%20as%20clan%20identity%C2%A0or%20for%20ritualistic%20purposes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062