luding%20those%20waiting%20for%20green%20cards%2C%20for%20five%20years%2C%20a%20move%20that%20would%20benefit%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Indians%20living%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20(USCIS)%20said%20it%20was%20increasing%20the%20maximum%20validity%20period%20of%20Employment%20Authorization%20Documents%20(EAD)%20to%205%20years%20for%20initial%20and%20renewal%20EADs%20for%20certain%20non-citizens%20who%20must%20apply%20for%20employment%20authorisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20applicants%20for%20asylum%20or%20withholding%20of%20removal%2C%20adjustment%20of%20status%20under%20INA%20245%2C%20and%20suspension%20of%20deportation%20or%20cancellation%20of%20removal%2C%20the%20federal%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20the%20maximum%20EAD%20validity%20period%20to%205%20years%20is%20intended%20to%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20new%20Forms%20I-765%2C%20Application%20for%20Employment%20Authorization%2C%20it%20receives%20for%20renewal%20EADs%20over%20the%20next%20several%20years%2C%20contributing%20to%20its%20efforts%20to%20reduce%20associated%20processing%20times%20and%20backlogs%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20whether%20the%20noncitizen%20maintains%20employment%20authorisation%20remains%20dependent%20on%20their%20underlying%20status%2C%20circumstances%2C%20and%20EAD%20filing%20category%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20an%20individual%20received%20an%20EAD%20under%20the%20category%20based%20on%20a%20pending%20adjustment%20of%20status%20application%20for%20the%20maximum%20validity%20period%20of%205%20years%2C%20and%20the%20adjustment%20application%20is%20then%20denied%2C%20their%20ancillary%20employment%20authorisation%20may%20be%20terminated%20before%20the%20expiration%20date%20listed%20on%20their%20EAD%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20new%20study%2C%20more%20than%2010.5%20lakh%20Indians%20are%20in%20the%20queue%20for%20an%20employment-based%20Green%20Card%20and%204%20lakh%20of%20them%20may%20die%20before%20they%20receive%20the%20much-sought-after%20legal%20document%20of%20permanent%20residency%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Green%20Card%2C%20known%20officially%20as%20a%20Permanent%20Resident%20Card%2C%20is%20a%20document%20issued%20to%20immigrants%20to%20the%20US%20as%20evidence%20that%20the%20bearer%20has%20been%20granted%20the%20privilege%20of%20residing%20permanently.%20The%20per-country%20caps%20are%20numerical%20limits%20on%20the%20issuance%20of%20green%20cards%20to%20individuals%20from%20certain%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20employment-based%20Green%20Card%20backlog%20reached%20a%20new%20record%20of%201.8%20million%20cases%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study%20by%20David%20J%20Bier%20of%20the%20Cato%20Institute%2C%20an%20American%20libertarian%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%201.1%20million%20of%20the%201.8%20million%20cases%20in%20the%20backlog%20are%20from%20India%20(63%20per%20cent).%20Another%20nearly%20250%2C000%20are%20from%20China%20(14%20per%20cent)%2C%20it%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697249700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-01%2Fstatue-of-liberty_650x400_61516584069.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fus-move-to-benefit-tens-of-thousands-of-indians-waiting-for-green-cards-4480066%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20has%20announced%20it%20will%20provide%20employment%20authorisation%20cards%20to%20some%20non-immigrant%20categories%2C%20including%20those%20waiting%20for%20green%20cards%2C%20for%20five%20years%2C%20a%20move%20that%20would%20benefit%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Indians%20living%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%