%20being%20the%20only%20Mizo%20to%20have%20the%20longest%20term%20on%20that%20high%20chair%20cumulatively.%20And%2C%20if%20by%20any%20chance%2C%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%2C%20fails%20to%20pocket%20a%20win%20in%20the%20November%207%20polls%2C%20he%20in%20all%20likelihood%20would%20walk%20into%20political%20retirement%20considering%20his%20advanced%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20and%20more%20significantly%2C%20these%20elections%20would%20help%20Mizoram%20break%20out%20of%20the%20typical%20mold%20of%20voters%20having%20to%20choose%20a%20chief%20minister%20only%20from%20two%20available%20choices.%20Since%201988%2C%20the%20contenders%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20chair%20were%20typically%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Lalthanhawla%20and%20Zoramthanga%20from%20the%20MNF%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Mizoram%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20(MPCC)%20now%20having%20a%20president%20a%20few%20years%20younger%20than%20the%20octogenarian%20Pu%20Hawla%20in%20Lalsawta%2C%20and%20the%20new%20and%20rising%20regional%20entity%2C%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM)%20having%20a%20face%2C%20Lalduhouma%2C%20who%20is%20also%20way%20younger%20to%20the%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%2079-year-old%20Zoramthanga%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20chief%20ministerial%20loop%20in%20that%20state%20is%20certainly%20getting%20a%20coat%20of%20sparkle%20and%20freshness%20this%20poll%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20strong%20credentials%20to%20back%20them%2C%20both%20Lalsawta%20and%20Lalduhouma%20are%20formidable%20claimants%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20too.%20Take%20Lalsawta.%20A%20former%20finance%20minister%20in%20the%20Lalthanhawla%20regime%2C%20Lalsawta%20has%20a%20clean%20public%20image.%20Political%20observers%20in%20the%20state%20believe%20that%20this%20three-time%20MLA%20could%20be%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20the%20state%2C%20particularly%20since%20the%20issue%20of%20Mizoram%20being%20a%20debt-ridden%20state%20is%20picking%20up%20traction%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20Congress%2C%20this%20past%20October%2011%2C%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Aizawl%20in%20response%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20earlier%20this%20week%20claiming%20that%20Mizoram%20stood%20second%20lowest%20in%20terms%20of%20debt%20in%20the%20country.%20Congress%20legislative%20party%20leader%20Zodintuanga%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmisleading%20and%20lying%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20projecting%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20debt%20with%20false%20parameters%E2%80%A6Looking%20at%20our%20present%20debt%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20to%20go%20beyond%2053.1%25%20even%20when%20the%20actual%20is%20out.%20This%20means%20that%20Mizoram%20will%20still%20have%20the%20highest%20debt%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Mizoram%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.themizorampost.net%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20press%20meet.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20face%20with%20proven%20credentials%20as%20a%20finance%20minister%20may%20cut%20some%20ice%20with%20the%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20candidates%20list%20but%20Lalsawta%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20Aizawl%20East%20II%20constituency%20which%20was%20wrested%20from%20him%20by%20MNF%20candidate%20R.R.%20Royte%20in%20the%202018%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ELalduhouma%20of%20ZPM%20too%20has%20a%20clean%20public%20image.%20For%20some%20months%20now%2C%20his%20party%20has%20been%20successful%20in%20catching%20voters%E2%80%99%20interest.%20Such%20an%20assessment%20of%20the%20local%20reporters%20and%20political%20observers%20particularly%20got%20credence%20after%20ZPM%20swept%20the%20Lunglei%20municipal%20elections%20held%20this%20past%20March-end.%20A%20former%20IPS%20officer%2C%20Lalduhouma%20is%20the%20founding%20president%20of%20ZPM%2C%20formed%20in%202017%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20last%20assembly%20elections.%20He%20had%20contested%20the%202018%20polls%20from%20two%20seats%20and%20succeeded%20in%20winning%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EIn%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20had%20secured%20six%20seats.%20Since%20it%20was%20not%20a%20registered%20party%2C%20all%20its%20candidates%20contested%20as%20independents.%20This%20election%20though%2C%20it%20is%20a%20recognised%20party%20and%20has%20already%20declared%20names%20for%20all%2040%20constituencies%20including%20Twichawng%20in%20the%20Chakma%20autonomous%20council%20area.%20All%20its%20six%20MLAs%20in%20the%20present%20assembly%20have%20tendered%20resignation%20from%20the%20house%20recently%20to%20avoid%20the%20possibility%20of%20their%20disqualification%20for%20contesting%20the%20coming%20elections%20under%20the%20ZPM%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20only%20thorn%20in%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20way%20to%20success%20is%20a%20lingering%20doubt%20though%20among%20a%20section%20of%20voters%20that%20the%20party%20is%20close%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20In%202017%2C%20ZPM%20was%20a%20three-party%20formation%2C%20coming%20forward%20as%20a%20choice%20for%20a%20non-Congress%20and%20non-MNF%20government.%20Later%2C%20three%20other%20parties%20including%20the%20Zoram%20Nationalist%20Party%2C%20a%20former%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20joined%20the%20alliance%2C%20thus%20firming%20up%20even%20further%20that%20closeness%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20not%20quite%20the%20choice%20in%20a%20Christian-majority%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-ahead-of-polls-mnfs-renewed-call-for-zo-unification-creates-political-flutter%5C%22%3EMizoram%3A%20Ahead%20of%20Polls%2C%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20Renewed%20Call%20for%20Zo%20Unification%20Creates%20Political%20Flutter%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20state%2C%20this%20correspondent%20has%2C%20however%2C%20noted%20a%20likely%20shift%20of%20voter%20sentiments%20towards%20MNF%20due%20to%20the%20Zoramthanga%20government%E2%80%99s%20all-out%20support%20to%20the%20larger%20cause%20of%20security%20and%20safety%20for%20the%20Zo%20people%2C%20not%20just%20by%20sheltering%20a%20sizeable%20number%20of%20refugees%20and%20leaders%20from%20conflict-ridden%20Myanmar%20for%20some%20time%20now%20but%20also%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20fleeing%20neighbouring%20Manipur.%20With%20the%20chief%20minister%20reiterating%20the%20issue%20time%20and%20again%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20MNF%20is%20banking%20on%20it%20hugely%20in%20the%20coming%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1-300x162.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1-1024x554.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662929%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22649%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20EastMojo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20factor%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMizoram%20is%20the%20only%20state%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20form%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own%20or%20be%20part%20of%20the%20incumbent%20government.%20Though%20MNF%20is%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20and%20North%20East%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NEDA)%2C%20Zoramthanga%20has%20kept%20it%20at%20a%20distance%20considering%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20pro-Hindutva%20stance.%20Post%20Manipur%20strife%2C%20the%20party%20will%20particularly%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20BJP%20this%20poll%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20doing%20what%20it%20is%20best%20at%20%E2%80%93%20stealing%20MLAs%20and%20leaders%20from%20other%20parties%20in%20the%20northeast.%20Before%20the%20last%20polls%2C%20it%20succeeded%20in%20taking%20away%20from%20Congress%20Budha%20Dhan%20Chakma%2C%20a%20former%20minister%20in%20the%20Lalthanhawla%20government.%20Budha%20Dhan%20helped%20the%20BJP%20open%20its%20account%20in%20the%20Mizoram%20assembly%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20election%2C%20it%20is%20taking%20away%20two%20MLAs%20from%20its%20ally%2C%20MNF.%20This%20past%20October%2011%2C%20assembly%20speaker%20and%20MNF%20leader%20L.%20Sailo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmorungexpress.com%2Fmizoram-speaker-resigns-to-contest-polls-on-bjp-ticket%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20he%20was%20denied%20a%20ticket%20by%20the%20party%20from%20the%20Chalfilh%20seat%20and%20at%20once%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20Though%20the%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20candidates%20list%20for%20the%20state%2C%20he%20is%20most%20likely%20contesting%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20from%20Mamit%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20past%20week%2C%20yet%20another%20MNF%20leader%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fformer-mizoram-minister-quits-mnf-joins-bjp-ahead-of-assembly-polls-101696677607753.html%5C%22%3EK.%20Beichhua%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20is%20also%20set%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20ticket.%20The%20former%20MNF%20minister%20seemed%20to%20have%20given%20out%20the%20gameplan%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20typical%20modus%20operandi%20that%20the%20national%20party%20has%20been%20following%20in%20the%20Christian-majority%20states.%20Beichhua%20told%20reporters%20that%20no%20political%20party%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20coming%20polls%20and%20that%20elected%20BJP%20MLAs%20will%20then%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20forming%20a%20new%20government.%20Something%20that%20the%20party%2C%20even%20with%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20MLAs%20had%20done%20in%20Meghalaya%20and%20Nagaland%2C%20facilitated%20by%20a%20friendly%20governor%20posted%20strategically%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697247019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13225738%2FThe-Wire-40.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-upcoming-assembly-polls-are-momentous-for-mizorams-political-history%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%201988%20to%20until%20last%20elections%2C%20Mizoram%20voters%20chose%20between%20Lalthanhawla%20and%20Zoramthanga%20for%20chief%20minister's%20post.%20However%2C%20that%20is%20set%20to%20change%20this%20time%20around%20with%20Lalsawta%20from%20Congress%20and%20ZPM's%20Lalduhouma%20joining%20the%20race.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-upcoming-assembly-polls-are-momentous-for-mizorams-political-history%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20urges%20US%20to%20'control'%20Israel%20to%20avert%20regional%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697246637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104411497%2Cimgsize-37054.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Firan-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war%