202023.%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%2FHandout%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsrael%20said%20it%20dropped%206%2C000%20bombs%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20during%20the%20first%20six%20days%20of%20war%20with%20Hamas.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThat's%20more%20bombs%20than%20the%20US-led%20coalition%20dropped%20in%20any%20month%20during%20the%20fight%20against%20ISIS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAllied%20forces%20dropped%205%2C000%20bombs%20in%20August%202017%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20their%20air%20campaign.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20been%20at%20war%20with%20Hamas%20for%20less%20than%20a%20week%2C%20and%20its%20forces%20are%20already%20expending%20a%20massive%20amount%20of%20ordnance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20six%20days%2C%20Israeli%20fighter%20jets%20dropped%20more%20bombs%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20than%20the%20US-led%20coalition%20dropped%20in%20any%20month%20of%20its%20fight%20against%20the%20Islamic%20State%2C%20even%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20multi-national%20air%20campaign%20against%20the%20terror%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20began%20its%20aerial%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20on%20Saturday%20immediately%20after%20Hamas%20militants%20launched%20a%20series%20of%20surprise%20terror%20attacks%20against%20the%20country%2C%20killing%20at%20least%201%2C300%20people%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20civilians%20%E2%80%94%20and%20injuring%20over%203%2C200%20more.%20The%20group%20also%20took%20an%20estimated%20150%20people%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIAFsite%2Fstatus%2F1712484101763342772%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20had%20dropped%20%26quot%3Babout%206%2C000%20bombs%20against%20Hamas%20targets%20in%20the%20densely%20populated%20coastal%20enclave.%26quot%3B%20The%20relentless%20campaign%2C%20which%20was%20ongoing%20as%20of%20Friday%20evening%20local%20time%2C%20has%20reduced%20entire%20