ensive%20in%20the%20Donbas%20region%20of%20eastern%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20this%20wasn't%20a%20surprise%2C%20given%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20goal%20of%20bringing%20Ukraine%20back%20into%20the%20Soviet%20sphere%20of%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20would%20add%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20Ukrainians%20work%20very%20hard%20to%20repel%20these%20offensive%20maneuvers%2C%20and%20they%20appear%20to%20have%20done%20just%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20also%20said%20North%20Korea%20recently%20sent%20Russia%201%2C000%20containers%20of%20military%20equipment%20and%20munitions%20and%20that%20it%20believes%20North%20Korea%20wants%20Russian%20military%20assistance%20in%20return%2C%20including%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20ballistic%20missile%20production%20equipment%2C%20and%20surface-to-air%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221203%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22russia%20north%20korea%20weapons%20routes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529a6296561dd877e7aa3be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22774%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKirby%20said%20the%20US%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20whether%20Moscow%20delivers%20on%20Pyongyang's%20expectations%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20already%20observed%20Russian%20ships%20offloading%20containers%20in%20the%20DPRK%2C%20which%20may%20constitute%20...%20the%20initial%20deliveries%20of%20material%20from%20Russia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKirby%20said%20that%20a%20military%20alliance%20between%20Russia%20and%20North%20Korea%20could%20undermine%20%26quot%3Bregional%20stability%20and%20the%20global%20nonproliferation%20regime%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20US%20is%20taking%20several%20steps%20in%20response%20to%20sanction%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20articl