y%20Society%20(BNHS)%20study%20found%201.2%20lakh%20Greater%20and%20Lesser%20flamingos%20(two%20species)%20in%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%94%20mainly%20the%20Thane%20creek%20%E2%80%94%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThane%20creek%2C%20which%20separates%20Mumbai%20island%20from%20the%20mainland%20is%20the%20key%20to%20this%20ecosystem%20and%20here%20is%20where%20the%20flamingos%20arrive%20from%20Kutch%20and%20some%20probably%20(the%20greater%20flamingos)%20all%20the%20way%20from%20the%20Persian%20gulf.%20Mumbai%20has%20such%20a%20beautiful%20mangrove%20and%20wetland%20habitat%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vidyasagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVisiting%20the%20numerous%20wetlands%20in%20the%20city%20and%20documenting%20the%20beautiful%20birds%20led%20to%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20about%20the%20issues%20around%20wetlands%20and%20the%20natural%20history%20phenomenon.%20He%20decided%20to%20create%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20conserving%20the%20urban%20wetlands%20through%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fflamingosofmumbai%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20page.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%2010%20pictures%20that%20show%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20preserve%20the%20mangroves%20and%20wetlands%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai.%20Image%20credit%3A%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-16