%20discussions%2C%20debates%2C%20and%20short%20story%20writing%20competitions!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJoin%20the%20club%20and%20become%20a%20part%20of%20their%20exciting%20activities%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstudents.iiserkol.ac.in%2F~debapriyo11033%2Flitclub%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Kochi%20Reads%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20evening%20from%204%20to%206%20pm%2C%20the%20Panampilly%20Nagar%20Park%20in%20Kochi%20is%20filled%20with%20colourful%20mats%20with%20devoted%20readers%20peering%20over%20their%20books.%20Gopika%20Manjusha%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20club%20says%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20favourite%20period%20in%20school%20was%20the%20library%20period%20%E2%80%94%20reading%20in%20silence%20with%20my%20friends%20sitting%20across%20the%20table.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20journey%20towards%20starting%20the%20club%20was%20inspired%20by%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Cubbon%20Reads.%20In%20its%20debut%20session%2C%20around%2015%20participants%20joined%20Gopika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20anticipating%20such%20a%20turnout%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Ffeatured%2Ftranquil-weekends-at-panampilly-park-book-lovers-haven%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20South%20First%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20never%20before%20seen%20people%20so%20absorbed%20in%20reading%20within%20a%20park%E2%80%99s%20ambience.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3EYou%20can%20join%20her%20club%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkochireads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20d