%20Levy%2C%20has%20bluntly%20said%20that%20if%20Israel%20%E2%80%9Cinvades%20Gaza%20it%20will%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20crimes%20of%20war%20Israel%20has%20ever%20committed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2021-minute%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Levy%2C%20who%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Punishment%20of%20Gaza%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20winner%20of%20the%20Olof%20Palme%20Prize%20and%20Sokolov%20Award%2C%20says%20if%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20threat%20%E2%80%9Cto%20change%20the%20Middle%20East%E2%80%9D%20and%20defence%20minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%E2%80%99s%20threat%20that%20%E2%80%9CGaza%20will%20never%20go%20back%20to%20what%20it%20was%E2%80%9D%20are%20implemented%2C%20Israel%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20brink%20of%20a%20wider%20war%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F4rxjT1jKqsQ%3Fsi%3DkMs7n24naUZR9o5R%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20very%20disturbing%20and%20depressing%20picture%20that%20he%20is%20painting%20of%20his%20country%E2%80%99s%20prospects%2C%20Levy%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20realism%20Israel%20needs%20a%20miracle%E2%80%9D%20adding%20the%20chances%20of%20that%20are%20very%20small.%20He%20said%20that%20people%20are%20in%20denial%20of%20their%20treatment%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20they%20have%20played%20with%20fire%20for%20years%2C%20if%20not%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELevy%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20bears%20very%20great%20responsibility%20for%20what%20happened%20and%20he%20must%20pay%20the%20price.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20moving%20steadily%2C%20if%20not%20acceleratedly%2C%20towards%20a%20climatic%20denouement%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20this%20morning%20announced%20that%20Israel%20wants%20all%20of%20Gaza%20north%20of%20Wadi%20Gaza%20to%20be%20vacated%20in%2024%20hours.%20That%E2%80%99s%201.1%20million%20people.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20has%20told%20these%20Gazans%20to%20evacuate%20to%20the%20south%20and%20only%20return%20when%20they%20are%20permitted%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20way%20Israel%20has%20treated%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20over%20the%20last%20several%20years%20or%20decades%2C%20he%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20fire%20at%20innocent%20people%2C%20take%20out%20people%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20and%20smash%20their%20faces%2C%20expel%2C%20confiscate%2C%20rob%2C%20grab%20people%20from%20their%20beds%2C%20carry%20out%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20continue%20with%20the%20unbelievable%20siege%20of%20the%20Gaza%20strip%2C%20and%20everything%20will%20be%20alright.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Levy%20asks%20of%20all%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20%E2%80%93%20and%20not%20just%20those%20of%20Gaza%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20is%20it%20possible%20to%20forget%20that%20these%20are%20human%20beings%20whose%20ancestors%20were%20expelled%20from%20their%20land%20and%20placed%20in%20refugee%20camps%20where%20they%20would%20remain%3F%20These%20were%20human%20beings%20whom%20Israel%20dispossessed%20and%20expelled%2C%20whom%20it%20conquered%20again%20in%20their%20land%20of%20refuge%20and%20then%20turned%20into%20animals%20in%20a%20cage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20to%20the%20future%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20do%20so%2C%20Levy%20asks%3A%20%E2%80%9CWill%20Israel%20learn%20its%20lesson%3F%20No.%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20threats%20of%20%E2%80%98flattening%20Gaza%E2%80%99%20prove%20only%20one%20thing%3A%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20learned%20a%20thing.%20The%20arrogance%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20even%20though%20Israel%20is%20paying%20a%20high%20price%20once%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697201632000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13182007%2FKT-13-oct-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-invading-gaza-israels-biggest-ever-war-crime-haaretz-columnist-gideon-levy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20Levey%20says%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20are%20in%20denial%20of%20their%20treatment%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20they%20have%20played%20with%20fire%20for%20years%2C%20if%20not%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-invading-gaza-israels-biggest-ever-war-crime-haaretz-columnist-gideon-levy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Any%20Indiscriminate%20Targeting%20of%20Civilians%20is%20a%20War%20Crime%2C%20Say%20UN%20Experts.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20Why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13174809%2FGaza-ruin.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cspan%3EBefore%20Israel%20gave%20just%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20notice%20to%201.1%20million%20Gazans%20to%20move%20out%20or%20face%20bombing%2C%2048%20UN%20human%20rights%20independent%20experts%20asserted%20that%20any%20violence%20that%20indiscriminately%20targets%20civilians%20would%20amount%20to%20a%20war%20crime%2C%20highlighting%20that%20international%20law%20has%20clear%20rules%20that%20define%20the%20conduct%20of%20any%20armed%20conflict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20around%20midnight%20Israel%20time%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20was%20notified%20by%20Israel%20that%20it%20had%2024%20hours%20to%20evacuate%20more%20than%20a%20million%20civilians%20from%20the%20northern%20half%20of%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20described%20the%20demand%20as%20%E2%80%9Cimpossible%E2%80%9D%20and%20carrying%20%E2%80%9Cdevastating%20humanitarian%20consequences%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20six%20days%20after%20Hamas%20fired%20rockets%20towards%20Israel%2C%20breached%20the%20border%20and%20targeted%20military%20personnel%20and%20civilians%2C%20including%20at%20a%20music%20festival.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%201%2C300%20Israelis%20and%20foreign%20citizens%20were%20killed%20and%20around%20150%20people%20have%20been%20taken%20hostage%20into%20Gaza%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UN%20experts%20condemned%20the%20%E2%80%9Chorrific%20crimes%E2%80%9D%20by%20Hamas%2C%20which%20included%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%20and%20widespread%20killing%20and%20hostage-taking%20of%20innocent%20civilians%2C%20including%20older%20persons%20and%20children%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20described%20the%20actions%2C%20including%20the%20hostage-taking%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cheinous%20violations%20of%20international%20law%20and%20international%20crimes%2C%20for%20which%20there%20must%20be%20urgent%20accountability%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20counter-attack%2C%20Israel%20immediately%20started%20bombing%20Gaza%2C%20killing%201%2C537%20Palestinians%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20displacing%20more%20than%20300%2C000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fsv7Wp2Fn_Ng%3Fsi%3D85lYxgLDMl4QIRpB%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2F2023%2F10%2Fisraeloccupied-palestinian-territory-un-experts-deplore-attacks-civilians%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20released%20with%20the%20signatures%20of%2048%20UN%20independent%20experts%2C%20said%20that%20the%20airstrikes%20on%20Gaza%20amounted%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccollective%20punishment%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20justification%20for%20violence%20that%20indiscriminately%20targets%20innocent%20civilians%2C%20whether%20by%20Hamas%20or%20Israeli%20forces.%20This%20is%20absolutely%20prohibited%20under%20international%20law%20and%20amounts%20to%20a%20war%20crime%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20experts%20noted%20that%20Gaza%20has%20%E2%80%9Clived%20under%20unlawful%20blockade%20for%2016%20years%2C%20and%20already%20gone%20through%20five%20major%20brutal%20wars%2C%20which%20remain%20unaccounted%20for%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20expressed%20concern%20about%20reports%20that%20journalists%20and%20media%20workers%20reporting%20on%20the%20conflict%20had%20been%20targeted%2C%20with%20seven%20Palestinian%20journalists%20and%20media%20workers%20reportedly%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20statement%20asserted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cindiscriminately%20killing%20civilians%20in%20the%20context%20of%20hostilities%2C%20with%20no%20regard%20for%20the%20principles%20of%20distinction%2C%20precaution%20and%20proportionality%2C%20is%20a%20war%20crime%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20experts%20had%20also%20expressed%20their%20shock%20at%20the%20language%20of%20the%20Israeli%20defence%20minister%20in%20cutting%20off%20essential%20supplies%20to%20Gaza%2C%20who%20had%20stated%20that%20the%20authorities%20are%20fighting%20%E2%80%9Chuman%20animals%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20this%20appalling%20language%20that%20dehumanises%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20have%20been%20unlawfully%20%E2%80%9Cimprisoned%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza%20for%2016%20years%2C%20we%20condemn%20the%20withholding%20of%20essential%20supplies%20such%20as%20food%2C%20water%2C%20electricity%20and%20medicines.%20Such%20actions%20will%20precipitate%20a%20severe%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20its%20population%20is%20now%20at%20inescapable%20risk%20of%20starvation.%20Intentional%20starvation%20is%20a%20crime%20against%20humanity%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20on%20Thursday%20had%20nuanced%20its%20initial%20response%20to%20the%20terror%20attack%20on%20Saturday%20by%20adding%20that%20Tel%20Aviv%20also%20had%20an%20obligation%20to%20follow%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Six%20Takeaways%20from%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20Conflict%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsix-takeaways-from-the-israel-palestine-conflict%5C%22%3ESix%20Takeaways%20from%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20Conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20international%20humanitarian%20law%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20Red%20Cross%2C%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20(IHL)%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.icrc.org%2Filot%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2Ftreaties-make-international-humanitarian-law%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edefined%20set%20of%20rules%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20seeks%2C%20for%20humanitarian%20reasons%2C%20to%20limit%C2%A0the%20effects%20of%20armed%20conflict%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0The%20concept%20of%20modern%20humanitarian%20law%20is%20more%20than%20150%20years%20old%2C%20with%20experts%20stating%20that%20it%20began%20with%20the%20Geneva%20Convention%20of%201864.%20The%20key%20treaties%20that%20form%20the%20foundation%20of%20IHL%20are%20the%201949%20Geneva%20Convention%20and%20its%20additional%20protocol%20signed%20in%201977.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20UN%20charter%2C%20which%20talks%20about%20whether%20a%20state%20can%20resort%20to%20armed%20force%2C%20IHL%20regulates%20the%20conduct%20of%20parties%20in%20an%20armed%20conflict%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejus%20in%20bello%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20applies%20to%20the%20current%20conflict%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EProtection%20of%20civilians%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20key%20underlying%20theme%20of%20IHL%20is%20that%20civilians%20should%20not%20be%20targeted%20in%20any%20conflict%20and%20must%20be%20distinguished%20from%20fighters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fihl-databases.icrc.org%2Fen%2Fihl-treaties%2Fapi-1977%2Farticle-57%3FactiveTab%3Dundefined%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erules%20of%20waging%20war%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%20advance%20warning%20shall%20be%20given%20of%20attacks%20which%20may%20affect%20the%20civilian%20population%2C%20unless%20circumstances%20do%20not%20permit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20gave%20a%20notice%20of%2024%20hours%20to%20remove%20more%20than%20a%20million%20people%20from%20north%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHuman%20Rights%20Watch%20stated%20that%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%E2%80%9D%20depends%20on%20the%20circumstances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20an%20assessment%20would%20take%20into%20account%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20warning%20and%20the%20ability%20of%20civilians%20to%20leave%20the%20area.%20A%20warning%20that%20does%20not%20give%20civilians%20adequate%20time%20to%20leave%20for%20a%20safer%20area%20would%20not%20be%20considered%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2Fquestions-and-answers-october-2023-hostilities-between-israel-and-palestinian-armed%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20the%20provision%20of%20the%20Additional%20Protocol%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20even%20after%20an%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%20advance%20warning%E2%80%9D%2C%20civilians%20should%20not%20be%20targeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20provision%20of%20this%20Article%20may%20be%20construed%20as%20authorizing%20any%20attacks%20against%20the%20civilian%20population%2C%20civilians%20or%20civilian%20objects%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icrc.org%2Fen%2Fdoc%2Fassets%2Ffiles%2Fother%2Ficrc_002_0321.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditional%20Protocol%20I%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20Article%2057%20on%20Precautions%20in%20Attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3ud__248-KY%3Fsi%3DenjncPnWumOaLBx4%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20Article%2055%20(b)%20also%20notes%20that%20an%20attack%20is%20prohibited%20in%20law%20if%20it%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20be%20expected%20to%20cause%20incidental%20loss%20of%20civilian%20life%2C%20injury%20to%20civilians%2C%20damage%20to%20civilian%20objects%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20thereof%2C%20which%20would%20be%20excessive%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20concrete%20and%20direct%20military%20advantage%20anticipated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERight%20to%20self-defence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UN%20charter%20prohibits%20all%20kinds%20of%20armed%20conflict%2C%20except%20in%20%E2%80%9Cself-defence%E2%80%9D.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20argument%20when%20it%20invaded%20Gaza%20in%20the%20past%20also%20relied%20upon%20the%20rules%20for%20going%20to%20war%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejus%20ad%20bellum%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fabout-us%2Fun-charter%2Fchapter-7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChapter%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20charter%20lists%20the%20%E2%80%9Cactions%20with%20respect%20to%20threats%20to%20the%20peace%2C%20breaches%20of%20the%20peace%2C%20and%20acts%20of%20aggression%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.culawreview.org%2Fjournal%2Fthe-self-defense-principle-re-examined-the-israel-palestine-conflict-in-international-law%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2021%20paper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20in%20the%20Columbia%20Law%20School%20Undergraduate%20Review%2C%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20definition%20in%20international%20law%20doctrine%20for%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Caggression%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20gives%20states%20leeway%20in%20justifying%20war.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20the%20paper%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20use%20of%20the%20self-defence%20argument%20also%20directly%20threatens%20the%20distinction%20between%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejus%20ad%20bellum%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejus%20in%20bello%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELaw%20of%20proportionality%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rule%20of%20proportionality%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20property%20was%20codified%20first%20in%20Additional%20Protocol%E2%80%99s%20Article%2051%20(5)%20(b)%2C%20which%20states%20that%20an%20attack%20would%20be%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cindiscriminate%E2%80%9D%20if%20it%20may%20be%20%E2%80%9Cexpected%20to%20cause%20incidental%20loss%20of%20civilian%20life%2C%20injury%20to%20civilians%2C%20damage%20to%20civilian%20objects%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20thereof%2C%20which%20would%20be%20excessive%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20concrete%20and%20direct%20military%20advantage%20anticipated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fimage.guardian.co.uk%2Fsys-files%2FGuardian%2Fdocuments%2F2009%2F09%2F15%2FUNFFMGCReport.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2009%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20fact-finding%20mission%20on%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20found%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20framing%20of%20Israeli%20military%20objectives%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20Gaza%20operations%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Csupporting%20infrastructure%E2%80%9D%20is%20particularly%20worrying%20as%20it%20appears%20to%20transform%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20objects%20into%20legitimate%20targets%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CStatements%20by%20Israeli%20political%20and%20military%20leaders%20prior%20to%20and%20during%20the%20military%20operations%20in%20Gaza%20indicate%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20conception%20of%20what%20was%20necessary%20in%20a%20war%20with%20Hamas%20viewed%20disproportionate%20destruction%20and%20creating%20the%20maximum%20disruption%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20many%20people%20as%20a%20legitimate%20means%20to%20achieve%20not%20only%20military%20but%20also%20political%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20two%20years%20later%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20fact-finding%20mission%20claimed%20that%20he%20would%20have%20written%20the%20report%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2Freconsidering-the-goldstone-report-on-israel-and-war-crimes%2F2011%2F04%2F01%2FAFg111JC_story.html%3Fhpid%3Dz3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edifferently%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20other%20three%20members%20of%20the%20mission%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcommentisfree