0%3Cem%3Elaabarthi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(beneficiaries)%20seem%20old%20and%20over-exhausted%2C%20especially%20when%20electoral%20considerations%20centre%20around%20state%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last-minute%20decision%20to%20pass%20the%20baton%20to%20Union%20ministers%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20BJP%20of%20yesteryears.%20Before%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20helmed%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20the%20organisation%20revelled%20in%20projecting%20a%20chief%20minister%20candidate%20in%20almost%20all%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20went%20to%20elections%20without%20it.%20Having%20a%20strong%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20was%20counted%20as%20one%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20strengths.%20Where%20have%20all%20the%20state-level%20leaderships%20disappeared%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20one%20is%20bound%20to%20ask.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20commentators%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20increasing%20centralisation%20of%20the%20party%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20has%20pushed%20the%20BJP%20into%20a%20corner.%20There%20is%20no%20leader%20in%20the%20party%20at%20the%20state%20level%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20barring%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20chief%20ministers%20Adityanath%20and%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20%E2%80%93%20who%20can%20proudly%20claim%20to%20have%20the%20state-wide%20support%20of%20the%20electorate.%20And%20it%20may%20be%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%E2%80%99s%20own%20doing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBW83ZtfcZ0Y%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20recent%20show%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20political%20commentator%20Abhay%20Kumar%20Dubey%20contended%20that%20the%20BJP%20under%20Modi%20is%20somewhat%20similar%20to%20the%20Congress%20under%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20systematically%20appointed%20pliant%20leadership%20in%20the%20states%20as%20a%20measure%20to%20concentrate%20all%20decision-making%20powers%20at%20the%20top%20level.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20Congress%20gradually%20weakened%20its%20own%20political%20position%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20giving%20way%20for%20opposition%20parties%20to%20fill%20that%20vacuum.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20concentrate%20powers%20in%20his%20own%20hands%20are%20accompanied%20by%20the%20great%20popularity%20that%20he%20enjoys%20both%20within%20the%20party%20and%20amidst%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20electorate%20%E2%80%93%20similar%20to%20how%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20perceived.%20The%20prime%20minister%20has%20also%20added%20a%20good%20dose%20of%20corporate%20work%20culture%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20functioning.%20Although%20such%20a%20work%20culture%20has%20shot%20up%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20efficiency%20in%20implementing%20its%20electoral%20strategy%20to%20a%20great%20extent%2C%20it%20has%20also%20weakened%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20feedback%20mechanisms.%20Added%20emphasis%20on%20professionalism%20has%20encouraged%20the%20promotion%20of%20those%20who%20can%20implement%20central%20strategies%20more%20efficiently%20than%20those%20who%20may%20be%20better%20placed%20to%20address%20state-level%20concerns.%20Such%20a%20delinking%20of%20central%20and%20state%20leaders%20has%20already%20started%20to%20show%20ominous%20signs%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20at%20least%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20leadership%20vacuum.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20a%20few%20instances%20of%20such%20a%20trend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20BJP%20nurtured%20Adivasi%20leaders%20like%20Arjun%20Munda%20and%20Babulal%20Marandi%20but%20when%20it%20won%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20it%20chose%20Raghubar%20Das%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20match%20either%20Munda%20or%20Marandi%E2%80%99s%20stature.%20The%20party%2C%20thus%2C%20had%20to%20face%20a%20massive%20defeat%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20polls%2C%20months%20after%20Modi%20steered%20his%20party%20to%20its%20biggest%20victory%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20sideline%20its%20tallest%20leader%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%20and%20appoint%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20cost%20the%20BJP%20a%20little%20too%20much%2C%20erasing%20the%20only%20footprint%20it%20has%20in%20southern%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20systematically%20taking%20away%20all%20power%20from%20former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20currently%20struggling%20to%20find%20her%20replacement%20in%20poll-bound%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20signs%20show%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20does%20not%20want%20the%20popular%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20to%20retain%20the%20seat%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20if%20it%20wins.%20In%20fact%2C%20throughout%20his%20last%20tenure%2C%20the%20state%20home%20minister%20Narottam%20Mishra%20was%20consulted%20much%20more%20than%20Chouhan%20in%20taking%20important%20decisions.%20That%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20leadership%20crisis%2C%20forcing%20the%20BJP%20to%20deploy%20Union%20ministers%20like%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20and%20MPs%20like%20Prahlad%20Patel%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20learn%20from%20what%20has%20clearly%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20disaster%2C%20and%20has%20increasingly%20attempted%20to%20cement%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20cult%20as%20its%20central%20electoral%20strategy%20rather%20than%20to%20empower%20popular%20leaders%20in%20the%20states.%20Even%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%2C%20the%20popular%20Anandiben%20Patel%20was%20replaced%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20by%20the%20little-known%20Vijay%20Rupani%20and%20now%20Bhupendrabhai%20Patel.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20the%20party%20ignored%20many%20top-level%20leaders%20to%20appoint%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20party%20chose%20a%20Brahmin%20leader%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20over%20popular%20leaders%20from%20other%20communities.%20Fadnavis%20hardly%20matches%20the%20stature%20of%20some%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20older%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F08103009%2FFyCLfb_WwAEq6JO.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F08103009%2FFyCLfb_WwAEq6JO.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F08103009%2FFyCLfb_WwAEq6JO-300x200.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-657095%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40Dev_Fadnavis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20appears%20to%20be%20following%20the%20same%20pattern%20even%20in%20organisational%20reshuffling.%20Recently%2C%20G.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20replaced%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20as%20the%20Telangana%20unit%20president.%20Sanjay%20had%20emerged%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20its%20own%20right%20and%20was%20credited%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20strong%20show%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20party%20overlooked%20leaders%20like%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20who%20built%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20unit%20in%20Bihar%20from%20scratch%20and%20has%20since%20then%20given%20prominence%20to%20polarising%20leaders%20like%20Giriraj%20Singh%20or%20turncoats%20like%20R.C.P.%20Singh.%20Although%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20popular%20chief%20minister%20in%20Assam%2C%20he%2C%20too%2C%20was%20preferred%20over%20long-time%20BJP%20leader%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal.%20Then%20in%20Punjab%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20senior%20leader%20Ashwini%20Sharma%20was%20replaced%20with%20the%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20as%20the%20state%20unit%E2%80%99s%20president%20%E2%80%93%20a%20decision%20that%20has%20ruffled%20feathers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20the%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20while%20fielding%20Union%20ministers%20in%20assembly%20polls%2C%20cited%20Modi%20as%20saying%20that%20he%20believed%20that%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20lead%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20campaigns%20for%20long%2C%20and%20that%20state%20leaderships%20would%20have%20to.%20There%20is%20a%20clear%20gap%20between%20what%20Modi%20is%20said%20to%20believe%20and%20the%20decisions%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20has%20taken%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20narrative%20clearly%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20match%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decisions.%20Modi%20will%20have%20to%20do%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20as%20long%20as%20he%20remains%20the%20sole%20leader%20of%20stature%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697196913000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13162841%2FH20231002140328.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-experimental-strategy-union-ministers-mps-assembly-elections-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22And%20given%20that%20the%20BJP's%20central%20electoral%20strategy%20continues%20to%20depend%20on%20the%20cult%20of%20Modi%2C%20the%20success%20of%20this%20model%20is%20far%20from%20guaranteed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2