is%20audience%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1964733%5C%22%3EPIB%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20need%20to%20not%20only%20combat%20terrorism%20but%20also%20dismantle%20its%20entire%20ecosystem%E2%80%9D.%20An%20ominously%20sweeping%20mandate%20for%20the%20policeman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3ESince%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20universally%20serenaded%20as%20the%20second%20most%20powerful%20man%20in%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20it%20is%20fair%20to%20assume%20that%20when%20he%20articulated%20the%20need%20for%20a%20new%20ruthlessness%20he%20was%20not%20just%20reflecting%20the%20ruling%20elite%E2%80%99s%20infatuation%20with%20coercion%20but%20also%20serving%20notice%20that%20henceforth%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctake-no-prisoners%E2%80%9D%20attitude%20would%20define%20their%20approach%20to%20political%20rivals%2C%20foes%20and%20dissenters.%20There%20is%20a%20new%20confidence%20that%20the%20regime%20will%20encounter%20no%20opposition%20as%20it%20pursues%20its%20chosen%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArguably%2C%20with%20nine%20years%E2%80%99%20experience%20under%20its%20belt%2C%20the%20Modi%20regime%20seems%20to%20have%20made%20a%20cool%20calculation%20that%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20will%2C%20occasionally%2C%20play%20to%20the%20gallery%20but%20there%20will%20never%20be%20any%20bite%20behind%20its%20bark.%20As%20long%20as%20the%20government%20keeps%20chanting%20its%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D%20mantra%2C%20it%20can%20go%20merrily%20about%20cherry-picking%20its%20real%20or%20presumed%20%E2%80%9Cenemies%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cecosystem%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%20anyone%20outside%20the%20inner%20cordon%20of%20%3Cem%3Eji%20hazoor%3C%2Fem%3E%20wallahs.%20A%20maximalist%20definition%20and%20interpretation%20of%20anti-terror%20laws%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20constitutionally%20protected%20rights%20shall%20be%20the%20order%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20politicians%20will%20always%20be%20politicians%20and%20inevitably%20play%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D%20game%20if%20it%20will%20fetch%20them%20a%20few%20extra%20votes%2C%20what%20is%20deeply%20disquieting%20is%20that%20the%20political%20crowd%20has%20effortlessly%20enlisted%20the%20enthusiastic%20complicity%20of%20thousands%20and%20thousands%20of%20%E2%80%98servants%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99.%20The%20vast%20infrastructure%20of%20national%20security%20has%20bought%20into%20this%20new%20theology%20of%20ruthlessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20Is%20the%20Indian%20State%20Reigniting%20a%2013-Year-Old%20Case%20Against%20Arundhati%20Roy%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-is-the-indian-state-reigniting-a-13-year-old-case-against-arundhati-roy%5C%22%3EWhy%20Is%20the%20Indian%20State%20Reigniting%20a%2013-Year-Old%20Case%20Against%20Arundhati%20Roy%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20familiar%20syndrome%20in%20history%20from%20the%20lands%20of%20totalitarianism.%20It%20is%20best%20decoded%20by%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20winner%2C%20Svetlana%20Alexievich%2C%20in%20%3Cem%3ESecond-Hand%20Time%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20when%20one%20of%20her%20interlocutors%20points%20out%20the%20incompleteness%20of%20blaming%20the%20Stalinist%20era%20excesses%20entirely%20on%20the%20Great%20Comrade.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20the%20victim%20and%20Stalin%20alone%20is%20to%20blame.%20But%20think%20about%20it%20%E2%80%A6it%E2%80%99s%20simple%20arithmetic%E2%80%A6Millions%20of%20inmates%20had%20to%20be%20surveilled%2C%20arrested%2C%20interrogated%2C%20transported%20and%20shot%20for%20minor%20transgressions.%20Someone%20had%20to%20do%20all%20this%E2%80%A6and%20they%20found%20millions%20of%20people%20who%20were%20willing%20to%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20just%20think%20of%20thousands%20and%20thousands%20of%20personnel%20in%20our%20own%20ever%20mushrooming%20%E2%80%9Cagencies%E2%80%9D%20doing%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20bidding%20without%20being%20told.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20new%20joy%20among%20our%20civil%20servants%20as%20they%20go%20after%20our%20%E2%80%9Cenemies%E2%80%9D.%20It%20must%20have%20required%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20imagination%20to%20zero%20in%20on%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20the%20worm%20in%20the%20ecosystem%20to%20be%20dealt%20with.%20And%C2%A0%20it%20would%20definitely%20have%20demanded%20some%20ingenuity%20to%20dust%20out%20a%2013-year-old%20FIR%20against%20Arundhati%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20new%20rulers%20and%20their%20bidders%20seem%20unfazed%20by%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20global%20reputation%20as%20one%20of%20our%20best%20creative%20voices.%20We%20seem%20to%20be%20proclaiming%20to%20the%20world%20at%20large%20that%20we%20do%20not%20care%20for%20international%20opprobrium.%20We%20are%20hard%20men%20and%20we%20are%20comfortable%20with%20our%20own%20heavy%20hand.%20No%20one%20dare%20mistake%20us%20for%20%E2%80%9Csofties%E2%80%9D%3B%20you%20poke%20us%20or%20even%20think%20of%20poking%20us%20and%20we%20shall%20come%20after%20you%20with%20all%20we%E2%80%99ve%20got.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20elite%20probably%20draws%20comfort%20from%20its%20derived%20wisdom%20that%20the%20middle%20classes%20are%20almost%20uniformly%20untroubled%20by%20the%20increasing%20and%20widening%20use%20of%20coercion%20in%20our%20society%2C%20especially%20because%20this%20coercion%20comes%20wrapped%20up%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20in%20judicial%20sanction.%20Middle%20classes%20have%20a%20sneaking%20admiration%20for%20the%20policeman%20who%20uses%20his%20truncheon%20to%20keep%20peace%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20pertinent%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20invitation%20to%20a%20new%20ruthless%20approach%20was%20unveiled%20days%20before%20the%20world%20learnt%20of%20the%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20show%20of%20strength%20in%20Gaza.%20Now%20the%20regime%20has%20creatively%20unleashed%20its%20vast%20network%20of%20disinformation%20and%20fake%20news%20to%20seek%20reinforcement%20of%20its%20majoritarian%20prejudices.%20Social%20media%20is%20flooded%20with%20%E2%80%9Cbad%20Islam%2C%20bad%20Muslims%E2%80%9D%20themes.%20As%20self-designated%20Vishwagurus%2C%20we%20are%20now%20custodians%20of%20global%20peace%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22When%20Will%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Arrest%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20the%20CIA%20and%20Joe%20Biden%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhen-will-the-delhi-police-arrest-ajit-doval-the-cia-and-joe-biden%5C%22%3EWhen%20Will%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Arrest%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20the%20CIA%20and%20Joe%20Biden%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20subtext%20of%20the%20new%20emphasis%20is%20that%20we%20(read%3A%20the%20majority%20community)%20live%20in%20a%20violent%20and%20uncertain%20world%2C%20flirting%20with%20chaos%20and%20aggression%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20secure%20the%20services%20of%20a%20strong%20man%2C%20a%20leader%20who%20will%20protect%20us%20against%20the%20vendors%20of%20disorder%20and%20instability.%20And%20the%20strong%20man%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20maximum%20authority%20and%20unfettered%20powers%20to%20go%20after%20all%20those%20in%20the%20ecosystem%20who%20provide%20aid%20and%20comfort%20to%20agents%20of%20chaos.%20This%20infatuation%20with%20the%20policeman%20and%20his%20%3Cem%3Edanda%3C%2Fem%3E%20seems%20to%20have%20seeped%20down%20to%20the%20lower%20levels%20of%20the%20civil%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20elite%2C%20now%20armed%20with%20the%20technology%20of%20total%20surveillance%2C%20has%20come%20to%20believe%20that%20every%20challenge%20of%20statecraft%20can%20be%20met%20effectively%20by%20the%20use%20of%20a%20heavy%20hand.%20The%20danger%20is%20that%20this%20calculus%20de-emphasises%20the%20time-tested%20tools%20of%20dialogue%2C%20conversation%20and%20debate%20in%20search%20of%20reconciliation%2C%20fairness%20and%20consensus%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20securing%20social%20harmony%2C%20political%20stability%20and%20emotional%20solidarity.%20Manipur%20has%20already%20shown%20the%20limits%20of%20duplicity%20and%20deceit%20as%20instruments%20of%20governance%20in%20Bharat%20that%20is%20India.%20Yet%20we%20remain%20persuaded%20of%20the%20uses%20of%20ruthlessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Tribune%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697191388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fit-turns-out-modis-amrit-kaal-is-also-a-ruthless-kaal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ruling%20elite%2C%20now%20armed%20with%20the%20technology%20of%20total%20surveillance%2C%20has%20come%20to%20believe%20that%20every%20challenge%20of%20statecraft%20can%20be%20met%20effectively%20by%20the%20use%20of%20a%20heavy%20hand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fit-turns-out-modis-amrit-kaal-is-also-a-ruthless-kaal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Missing%20peace%20activist%20Vivian%20Silver%20-%20son%20awaits%20news%2C%20good%20or%20bad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697190818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0E11%2Fproduction%2F_131410630_viviansilverfamily.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw