%2FIMG_4740.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20hall%20of%20the%20India%20International%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Terrace%20Pergola%20was%20hushed%20on%20October%208%20as%20a%20handful%20of%20folks%20arrived%20early%20to%20pay%20their%20homage%20to%20Ustad%20Ali%20Zaki%20Hader%2C%20the%20Rudra%20veena%20exponent%20who%20breathed%20his%20last%20exactly%20a%20month%20earlier%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jamia%20Nagar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAli%20Zaki%20Hader%20was%20the%20adopted%20son%20of%20the%20late%20Rudra%20veena%20maestro%20Ustad%20Asad%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20who%20trained%20him%20from%20childhood%20in%20this%20difficult%20discipline.%20The%20young%20ustad%2C%20who%20turned%2050%20on%20April%2018%20this%20year%2C%20was%20the%20only%20recognised%20performer%20of%20the%20Khandahar%20bani%20of%20the%20Jaipur%20beenkar%20gharana%2C%20a%20tradition%20within%20the%20Dhrupad%20genre.%20His%20demise%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20a%20tradition.%20But%20that%20searing%20truth%20became%20an%20indelible%20image%20when%20his%20disciples%20and%20family%20brought%20in%20his%20veena%20and%20placed%20it%20carefully%20behind%20the%20photo%20of%20the%20late%20Zaki%20Hader.%20Reverently%2C%20they%20garlanded%20the%20photo%20of%20their%20beloved%20ustad%2C%20and%20they%20garlanded%20his%20beloved%20veena%2C%20custom-made%20decades%20earlier%20just%20for%20him.%20There%20could%20not%20have%20been%20a%20more%20telling%20realisation%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20instrument%20would%20resonate%20no%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShashi%20Bhushan%20opened%20the%20sombre%20gathering%2C%20after%20which%20Ustad%20Bahuddin%20Dagar%2C%20young%20Rudra%20veena%20representative%20of%20the%20famed%20Dagarvani%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20pillar%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Hader%20family%2C%20also%20spoke%20briefly.%20His%20words%20were%20quiet%20and%20sorrowful%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20departed%20but%20for%20the%20musical%20lineage%20that%20had%20been%20allowed%20to%20evaporate.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20way%2C%20we%20all%20failed%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20He%20then%20played%20for%20a%20short%20while%2C%20accompanied%20on%20the%20pakhawaj%20by%20Ustad%20Mohan%20Shyam%20Sharma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13150236%2FIMG_4737.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13150236%2FIMG_4737.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13150236%2FIMG_4737-300x230.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679932%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22765%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sadness%20of%20the%20occasion%2C%20heightened%20by%20the%20solemnity%20of%20the%20raga%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ealaap%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20resonated%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20the%20listeners%2C%20who%20included%20young%20and%20old%20friends%2C%20and%20students%20of%20music.%20Bahauddin%E2%80%99s%20strings%20seemed%20to%20sing%20quietly%20of%20the%20subtle%20truths%20that%20can%20be%20felt%20but%20not%20verbalised.%20The%20music%20of%20the%20Rudra%20veena%20is%20perhaps%20as%20close%20as%20one%20could%20imagine%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eanhad%20naad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(the%20unheard%20cosmic%20sound).%20Music%20critic%20Manjari%20Sinha%2C%20remarking%20how%20Asad%20Ali%20Khan%20used%20to%20liken%20the%20subtleness%20of%20a%20musical%20note%20to%20a%20wafting%20perfume%2C%20said%20that%20Zaki%E2%80%99s%20life%20had%20ended%20just%20as%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20take%20musical%20flight.%20If%20India%E2%80%99s%20classical%20arts%20require%20years%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esadhana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20penance%2C%20then%20the%20Rudra%20veena%20exacts%20the%20most%20trying%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esadhana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20all.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20perhaps%20why%20this%20music%20is%20too%20difficult%2C%20meditative%2C%20and%20demanding%20of%20total%20presence%20by%20both%20exponent%20and%20listener%2C%20to%20be%20widely%20popular.%20But%20these%20qualities%2C%20in%20a%20country%20that%20prides%20itself%20as%20the%20ground%20where%20the%20Vedas%20originated%2C%20should%20make%20it%20all%20the%20more%20precious.%20Its%20practitioners%2C%20as%20reservoirs%20of%20an%20ephemeral%20oral%20tradition%2C%20surely%20deserve%20more%20support%20than%20the%20thousands%20of%20other%20artists%20who%20practise%20more%20robust%20traditions%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20superficial%20times.%20It%20is%20a%20knowledge%20source%20to%20be%20particularly%20protected%20by%20those%20empowered%20to%20promote%20the%20arts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBahauddin%20and%20others%20including%20Shashi%20reminded%20the%20audience%20that%20though%20the%20worst%20neglect%20had%20happened%20to%20bring%20Zaki%20Hader%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20lineage%20to%20an%20end%2C%20we%20should%20all%20be%20mindful%20as%20a%20society%20that%20the%20same%20mistake%20not%20be%20repeated%20with%20other%20artists.%20Shashi%20in%20particular%20delivered%20an%20impassioned%20plea%20towards%20the%20close%20of%20the%20proceedings.%20Artists%20can%20be%20found%20on%20nearly%20every%20corner%20and%20side%20street%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20and%20supporting%20one%E2%80%99s%20local%20artists%20by%20taking%20lessons%20or%20seeing%20to%20their%20needs%20would%20only%20bring%20immense%20satisfaction%2C%20not%20monetary%20loss%2C%20to%20ordinary%20citizens.%20Not%20everyone%20can%20or%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20successful%20performer%2C%20but%20music%20in%20itself%20is%20a%20great%20healer%2C%20he%20emphasised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20many%20readers%2C%20the%20mention%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20tradition%20may%20be%20just%20words%20with%20little%20significance%2C%20because%20most%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20a%20musical%20gharana%20is%2C%20or%20what%20a%20Rudra%20veena%20is%20for%20that%20matter.%20However%2C%20even%20an%20ordinary%2C%20musically%20untrained%20person%20understands%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20in%20need%20of%20shelter%20and%20the%20most%20basic%20human%20necessities.%20The%20painful%20lack%20of%20these%20necessities%20shadowed%20not%20just%20the%20last%20days%20but%20the%20last%20years%20of%20Zaki%20Hader%E2%80%99s%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBehind%20the%20death%20of%20the%20Khandahar%20bani%20and%20its%20last%20living%20representative%20lies%20a%20story%20of%20neglect%20and%20a%20strangely%20duplicitous%20culture.%20As%20a%20country%2C%20we%20officially%20project%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20an%20exalted%20image%20of%20a%20living%20ancient%20civilisation%20that%20has%20seamlessly%20evolved%20into%20modern%20times.%20In%20reality%2C%20the%20genuine%20representatives%20of%20that%20ancient%20culture%20%E2%80%93%20the%20beenkars%2C%20the%20handloom%20weavers%2C%20the%20potters%20and%20the%20carpet%20knotters%20to%20name%20just%20a%20few%20%E2%80%93%20are%20relegated%20to%20dark%20corners%20of%20the%20collective%20psyche%20or%20to%20incidental%20videos%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Ali%20Zaki%20Hader%20died%20suddenly%20on%20September%208%2C%202023%2C%20his%20three%20disciples%2C%20Prasad%2C%20Shashi%20Bhushan%20and%20Yogesh%2C%20fulfilled%20their%20duties%20to%20their%20guru%20in%20full%20measure.%20They%20participated%20in%20the%20funeral%20preparations%2C%20helped%20carry%20him%20on%20his%20final%20journey%2C%20and%20importantly%2C%20were%20constantly%20by%20the%20side%20of%20his%20bereaved%20sister%20Shazia.%20In%20his%20lifetime%20also%2C%20these%20disciples%20helped%20him%20with%20financial%2C%20practical%20and%20moral%20support%2C%20through%20the%20daily%20challenges%20of%20life%20in%20urban%20India.%20Rent%2C%20paperwork%2C%20groceries%2C%20utility%20bills%20%E2%80%93%20these%20mundane%20requirements%20pave%20a%20thorny%20path%20to%20the%20stage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20also%20other%20people%20from%20various%20walks%20of%20life%20who%20despite%20having%20no%20relationship%20with%20the%20musical%20world%2C%20helped.%20There%20was%20the%20advocate%20who%20filed%20appeals%20on%20behalf%20of%20Hader%20when%20he%20was%20requesting%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20residence%20in%20Khel%20Gaon%C2%A0under%20the%20artists%E2%80%99%20quota%2C%20in%20the%20flat%20that%20had%20been%20allotted%20to%20his%20deceased%20guru.%20Lawyers%20are%20not%20known%20for%20attachment%20to%20their%20clients%2C%20or%20for%20being%20overly%20reverent.%20But%20this%20young%20man%2C%20having%20lost%20the%20case%20after%20years%20of%20effort%2C%20was%20present%20like%20a%20son%20of%20the%20family%20at%20the%20last%20rites.%C2%A0For%20the%20rest%2C%20there%20were%20neighbours%20and%20a%20few%20distant%20relatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20apartment%20into%20which%20Ali%20Zaki%20Hader%20and%20his%20sister%20moved%20after%20vacating%20the%20Khel%20Gaon%20flat%20was%20minuscule.%20Located%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20a%20multistorey%20building%20among%20the%20lanes%20of%20Jamia%20Nagar%2C%20it%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20many%20constructions%20carved%20up%20into%20tiny%20flats%20that%20serve%20as%20income%20generators%20for%20their%20owners%20in%20a%20market%20where%20the%20supplier%20has%20the%20upper%20hand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13150254%2FIMG_5957.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13150254%2FIMG_5957.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13150254%2FIMG_5957-300x238.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13150254%2FIMG_5957-410x325.jpg%20410w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679934%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22635%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAli%20Zaki%20Hader.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jamia%20Nagar%20residence%20provided%20barely%20enough%20space%20for%20the%20ustad%20and%20his%20sister%20%E2%80%94%20two%20small%20rooms%20within%20which%20to%20practise%2C%20teach%2C%20live%2C%20eat%20and%20sleep.%20Therefore%2C%20some%20of%20Hader%E2%80%99s%20heirloom%20instruments%20had%20been%20stored%20on%20his%20request%20in%20locations%20where%20they%20would%20be%20willingly%20and%20carefully%20looked%20after%20until%20his%20situation%20stabilised%20%E2%80%94%20a%20hope%20that%20was%20belied.%C2%A0%20The%20mythological%20grandeur%20of%20the%20Rudra%20veena%E2%80%99s%20history%20dwarfs%20such%20quarters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgain%20and%20again%2C%20the%20same%20questions%20arise.%20What%20do%20we%20mean%20as%20a%20nation%20when%20we%20refer%20to%20our%20%E2%80%98rich%20culture%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20soul-cleansing%20power%20of%20our%20arts%2C%20yet%20allow%20our%20greatest%20artists%20to%20languish%20in%20indigence%3F%20For%20what%20do%20our%20cultural%20institutions%20exist%2C%20if%20they%20are%20helpless%20in%20the%20face%20of%20an%20artist%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20to%20keep%20body%20and%20soul%20together%3F%20The%20Sangeet%20Natak%20Akademi%2C%20All%20India%20Radio%2C%20Doordarshan%2C%20numerous%20regional%20bodies%20representing%20the%20map%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20state%20Akademies%20and%20departments%20%E2%80%93%20the%20list%20is%20extensive%20%E2%80%93%20are%20publicly%20funded%20bodies.%20Do%20their%20officials%20have%20no%20duty%20to%20reach%20out%20to%2C%20or%20even%20search%20for%2C%20if%20they%20profess%20ignorance%2C%20highly%20qualified%20artists%20in%20need%20of%20financial%20support%3F%20To%20help%20keep%20alive%20a%20tradition%20bombastically%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98ancient%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98sacred%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98profound%E2%80%99%2C%20are%20they%20incapable%20of%20doing%20even%20as%20much%20as%20three%20or%20four%20dazed%20young%20men%20and%20a%20bunch%20of%20sorrowing%20neighbours%20did%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20manuscript%20of%20his%20forthcoming%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EGlimpses%20of%2020th%20Century%20Hindustani%20Music%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20well-known%20author%20and%20musicologist%20Deepak%20Raja%20states%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Rudra%20Veena%20is%20irreversibly%20headed%20for%20the%20museums%2C%20with%20a%20steadily%20depleting%20reservoir%20of%20musicianship.%20The%20first%20half%20of%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20saw%20the%20departure%20of%20twenty-one%20significant%20Beenkars.%20In%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%2C%20ten%20significant%20Beenkars%20departed%20from%20the%20scene.%20And%20the%20first%20decade%20of%20the%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Est%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20witnessed%20the%20demise%20of%20two%20significant%20beenkars.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20text%20was%20written%20in%20June%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAli%20Zaki%20Hader%E2%80%99s%20name%20can%20now%20be%20included%20in%20those%20dismal%20numbers.%20How%20many%20more%20valuable%20specimens%20of%20our%20intangible%20heritage%20will%20we%20lose%20before%20a%20healthy%20collaboration%20is%20created%20between%20government%20bodies%2C%20artists%2C%20the%20wealthy%20corporate%20sector%20(that%20has%20influence%20in%20health%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20housing)%20and%20civil%20society%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20a%20collaboration%2C%20shorn%20of%20political%20expediency%20and%20executed%20by%20knowledgeable%20as%20well%20as%20objective%20stewards%2C%20could%20repair%20our%20damaged%20cultural%20scene.%20It%20could%20be%20the%20only%20real%20tribute%20to%20Ali%20Zaki%20Hader%2C%20a%20musician%20who%20was%20forced%20to%20put%20his%20heirloom%20instruments%20on%20sale%20to%20meet%20his%20mortal%20needs.%20No%20one%20bought%20them.%20No%20one%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20noticed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanjana-rajan%5C%22%3EAnjana%20Rajan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20been%20writing%20on%20the%20arts%2C%20literature%20and%20society%20for%20nearly%2020%20years.%20She%20is%20a%20former%20deputy%20editor%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Hindu%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%2C%20a%20dance%20exponent%20and%20theatre%20practitioner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697190358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13150244%2FIMG_4740.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fwith-ali-zaki-hader-a-musical-tradition-dies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20adopted%20son%20of%20the%20late%20Rudra%20veena%20maestro%20Ustad%20Asad%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20the%20only%20recognised%20performer%20of%20the%20Khandahar%20bani%20of%20the%20Jaipur%20beenkar%20gharana%2C%20a%20tradition%20within%20the%20Dhrupad%20genre.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fwith-ali-zaki-hader-a-musical-tradition-dies%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%203%20Years%2C%20Gujarat%20Govt%20Hired%20Nearly%2035k%20State%20Buses%20for%20PM%2C%20CM%20Events%3B%20Owes%20Rs%2022%20Crore%20in%20Dues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13133530%2FThe_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_at_the_laying_of_foundation_stone_and_dedication_to_the_Nation_of_Multiple_Projects_worth_over_Rs._8000_crore_at_Amod_Bharuch_in_Gujarat_on_October_10_2022_2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F13%2Fgujarat-unpaid-bill-for-hiring-state-buses-spirals-in-3-yrs-2623528.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520government%2520said%2520that%2520in%2Care%2520yet%2520to%2520be%2520paid.%5C%22%3Enot%20paid%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20Rs%2022%20crore%20in%20rent%20for%20public%20transport%20buses%20that%20were%20hired%20to%20ferry%20people%20to%20events%20that%20were%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20or%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%20over%20the%20past%20three%20financial%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20numbers%20were%20revealed%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20raised%20by%20Congres%20MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly.%20The%20data%20also%20showed%20that%20while%20only%20122%20buses%20were%20used%20in%202020-21%20to%20bring%20people%20to%20government%20programmes%20that%20Modi%20or%20the%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20attended%2C%20this%20ballooned%20to%2031%2C211%20in%202022-23.%20In%202020-21%2C%20fewer%20events%20would%20have%20been%20held%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%20and%20subsequent%20restrictions%20on%20physical%20gatherings.%20Vijay%20Rupani%20and%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20have%20been%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Gujarat%20during%20that%20three-year%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(GSRTC)%20said%20that%20a%20total%20of%2034%2C868%20buses%20were%20allocated%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20events%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20paid%20Rs%2014.27%20lakh%20as%20rent%20for%20the%20buses%20during%202020-21%20and%20Rs%208.21%20crore%20for%202021-22.%20But%20Rs%2074.43%20lakh%20remained%20unpaid.%20In%202022-23%2C%20the%20government%20paid%20Rs%2086%20crore%20for%20using%20the%20buses%20but%20Rs%2021.41%20crore%20still%20remains%20unpaid.%20In%20total%2C%20the%20dues%20pending%20are%20Rs%2022.16%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20transport%20department%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cproceedings%20for%20the%20recovery%20of%20dues%20are%20in%20progress%20with%20the%20departments%20concerned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20Gujarat%20Congress%20MLA%2C%20Kanti%20Kharadi%2C%20asked%20how%20many%20buses%20were%20rented%20to%20carry%20people%20to%20state%20government%20programmes%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20the%20ones%20involving%20the%20PM%20or%20the%20CM%20%E2%80%93%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%20(2020-21%20to%202022-23)%20and%20how%20much%20rent%20was%20due.%20The%20response%20said%20that%2021%2C964%20ST%20buses%20were%20assigned%20for%20government%20programmes%20in%202020-21%2C%206%2C898%20in%202021-22%2C%20and%2038%2C868%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20government%20paid%20Rs%20112%20crore%20to%20GSRTC%20for%20the%20buses%20hired%20during%20that%20three-year%20period%2C%20while%20Rs%2041.01%20crore%20is%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKharadi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F13%2Fgujarat-unpaid-bill-for-hiring-state-buses-spirals-in-3-yrs-2623528.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520government%2520said%2520that%2520in%2Care%2520yet%2520to%2520be%2520paid.%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20%E2%80%9Cwasted%20people%E2%80%99s%20money%20on%20political%20programmes%20without%20paying%20the%20rent%2C%20which%20is%20cheating%20with%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CState%20transport%20buses%20are%20meant%20for%20transporting%20rural%20people%2C%20not%20to%20gather%20crowds%20for%20government%20events.%20The%20rural%20transport%20is%20hit%20when%20the%20government%20hires%20ST%20buses%20on%20a%20big%20scale%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697188527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13133530%2FThe_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_at_the_laying_of_foundation_stone_and_dedication_to_the_Nation_of_Multiple_Projects_worth_over_Rs._8000_crore_at_Amod_Bharuch_in_Gujarat_on_October_10_2022_2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-government-public-transport-buses-rent-dues-pm-cm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20transport%20department%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cproceedings%20for%20the%20recovery%20of%20dues%20are%20in%20progress%20with%20the%20departments%20concerned.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-government-public-transport-buses-rent-dues-pm-cm%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Street%20Artist%20Banksy%E2%80%99s%20Identity%20May%20Be%20Revealed%20in%20an%20Upcoming%20Lawsuit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F11172003%2F7983278280_be50c5245c_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20graffiti%20artist%20known%20as%20Banksy%20might%20be%20unmasked%20in%20an%20upcoming%20defamation%20case%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standard.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fbanksy-sued-instagram-post-guess-full-colour-black-b1111802.html%5C%22%3Ehis%20use%20of%20Instagram%20to%20invite%20shopl