ng%20vandalism%2C%20property%20destruction%2C%20criminal%20mischief%20or%20worse%20charges%20against%20the%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGunningham%20revealing%20himself%20would%20also%20destroy%20the%20Banksy%20mystique.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20snitch%20on%20himself%20or%20damage%20the%20brand.%20The%20more%20important%20reason%20Gunningham%20being%20Banksy%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20is%20because%20there%20is%20no%20Banksy%20%E2%80%93%20no%20individual%20who%20is%20Banksy%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20collective%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20time%2C%20there%20was%20one%20Banksy%20who%20had%20a%20graffiti%20career%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DulOiB3xEkzM%5C%22%3Efamous%20%E2%80%9Cbeef%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20subculture%20with%20London%20graffiti%20legend%20Robbo%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20time%20is%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglasgowtransmission.wordpress.com%2F2021%2F04%2F04%2Fbanksy-everything-that-is-defo-or-may-or-may-not-be-true%2F%5C%22%3EBanksy%20is%20now%20a%20collective%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20artists%20who%20work%20together%20to%20produce%20thoughtful%2C%20provocative%20and%20subversive%20pieces%20and%20installations.%20The%20scope%20and%20secrecy%20of%20Banksy%E2%80%99s%20larger%20works%20require%20the%20cooperation%20of%20many%20individuals%20to%20orchestrate%2C%20direct%20and%20produce%20them.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cbemusement%20park%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdismaland.co.uk%2F%5C%22%3EDismaland%3C%2Fa%3E(a%20sinister%20take%20on%20Disneyland-style%20theme%20parks)%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwalledoffhotel.com%2Fquestions.html%5C%22%3EWalled%20Off%20Hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Banksy%E2%80%99s%20hotel%20and%20commentary%20on%20the%20Israel%2FPalestine%20conflict)%20in%20Palestine%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBetter_Out_Than_In%5C%22%3EBetter%20Out%20Than%20In%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Banksy%E2%80%99s%20New%20York-wide%20art%20residence)%20are%20examples%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglasgowtransmission.wordpress.com%2F2021%2F04%2F04%2Fbanksy-everything-that-is-defo-or-may-or-may-not-be-true%2F%5C%22%3EInvestigators%20believe%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20collective%20includes%20many%20well-known%20and%20established%20artists.%20Bristol%20street%20artist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.john-doh.co.uk%2F%5C%22%3EJohn%20D%E2%80%99oh%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20among%20those%20rumoured%20to%20be%20involved%2C%20as%20is%20graffiti%20and%20street%20artist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ame72.com%2F%5C%22%3EJames%20AME72%20Ame%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20perhaps%20even%20Massive%20Attack%20singer%20Robert%20Del%20Naja%2C%20among%20others.%20This%20is%20speculation.%20And%20again%2C%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20matters%20is%20why%20Banksy%20has%20been%20in%20the%20courts%20recently.%20More%20important%20than%20the%20current%20defamation%20suit%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.lbr.cloud%2Fpublic%2F2021-05%2Fbanksy%2520monkey%2520trademark%2520cancellation.pdf%3FPjoCw7xOfeYRlSa6qorTXr9hkL4QcK1Y%3D%5C%22%3E2021%20rejection%20of%20Banksy%E2%80%99s%20trademark%20by%20the%20EU%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20the%20result%20of%20Banksy%E2%80%99s%20battle%20with%20street%20art%20greeting%20card%20producer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Farts-entertainment%2Fart%2Fnews%2Fbanksy-flower-thrower-lawsuit-full-colour-black-trademark-copyright-identity-b464781.html%5C%22%3EFull%20Colour%20Black%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20used%20Banksy%E2%80%99s%20image%20of%20a%20Monkey%20wearing%20a%20placard%20without%20permission.%20The%20ruling%20uses%20Banksy%E2%80%99s%20own%20words%20in%20the%20decision%2C%20stating%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20notes%20that%20the%20street%20artist%20explicitly%20stated%20that%20the%20public%20is%20morally%20and%20legally%20free%20to%20reproduce%2C%20amend%20and%20otherwise%20use%20any%20copyright%20works%20forced%20upon%20them%20by%20third%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.artnet.com%2Fart-world%2Fbanksy-trademark-full-colour-black-1971339%5C%22%3Ecopyright%20is%20for%20losers%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20Banksy%20said%20in%20his%20own%202017%20book%2C%20Wall%20and%20Piece.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20to%20declare%20the%20trademark%20invalid%20was%20filed%20in%202018.%20Banksy%20took%20great%20umbrage%20at%20this.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbanksyexplained.com%2Fgross-domestic-product-2019%2F%5C%22%3EOctober%20of%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20officially%20revealed%20the%20%E2%80%9Chomewares%E2%80%9D%20brand%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product.%20The%20store%20is%20officially%20the%20website%2C%20but%20it%20debuted%20as%20a%20pop-up%20shop%20which%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20entered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20posted%20on%20the%20pop-up%20%E2%80%9Cstorefront%E2%80%9D%20declared%20that%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product%20was%20opened%20in%20direct%20response%20to%20the%20trademark%20cancellation%20filing%20and%20that%20selling%20Banksy%20%E2%80%9Cbranded%20merchandise%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20best%20way%20to%20ensure%20ownership%20and%20control%20of%20the%20Banksy%20name.%20What%E2%80%99s%20important%20here%20is%20the%20clear%20interest%20in%20wanting%20to%20maintain%20control%20over%20what%20is%20and%20is%20not%20a%20Banksy%20and%20what%20Banksy%20artwork%20is%20associated%20with%20in%20commercial%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20team%20of%20professionals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBanksy%20fakes%20are%20everywhere.%20The%20artist%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20bulk%20of%20Banksy%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20stencils%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20easily%20reproduced%20by%20anyone%20with%20some%20talent%2C%20time%20and%20an%20Exacto%20knife%20%E2%80%93%20ensure%20fakes%20and%20copies%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20made.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20Banksy%20has%20a%20cohort%20of%20trusted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.artnet.com%2Fartists%2Fbanksy%2Fdealers%5C%22%3Eart%20dealers%20for%20official%20Banskys%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20authentication%20service%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpestcontroloffice.com%2F%5C%22%3EPest%20Control%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20chases%20and%20legitimates%20the%20provenance%20of%20Banskys.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20entirely%20legitimate%20for%20any%20artist%20to%20want%20to%20maintain%20their%20unique%20identity%20and%20control%20over%20their%20artwork%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20rare%20for%20an%20artist%20to%20maintain%20an%20entire%20staffed%20department%20dedicated%20to%20it.%20Not%20that%20graffiti%20writers%20don%E2%80%99t%20defend%20their%20copyrights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41599-018-0179-4%5C%22%3ERevok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.artnet.com%2Fart-world%2Ffutura-sures-north-face-copyright-infringement-1936871%5C%22%3EFutura%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwwd.com%2Ffashion-news%2Fdesigner-luxury%2Fstreet-artist-rime-jeremy-scott-moschino-copyright-lawsuit-settlement-10476118%2F%5C%22%3ERime%3C%2Fa%3E%20(to%20name%20a%20few)%20have%20defended%20their%20ownership%20of%20their%20graffiti%20and%20art%20in%20court.%20They%20hired%20lawyers%2C%20but%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20division%20dedicated%20to%20preempting%20and%20preventing%20infringement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPest%20Control%20is%20seemingly%20in%20place%20to%20maintain%20the%20authentic%20and%20unique%20perspective%20of%20Banksy%E2%80%99s%20works%20and%20to%20confirm%20they%20were%20officially%20produced%20by%20Banksy.%20This%20is%20a%20process%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20brand%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20the%20point%20of%20all%20this%3F%20Well%2C%20Banksy%20was%20an%20individual%20street%20artist%20at%20one%20point.%20This%20was%20probably%20Robin%20Gunningham.%20However%2C%20Banksy%20is%20now%20a%20collective%20of%20artists%20who%20work%20under%20the%20Banksy%20brand%20to%20produce%20the%20works%20that%20the%20Banksy%20authentication%20service%2C%20Pest%20Control%2C%20officially%20decrees%20as%20Banksys.%20Banksy%20is%20also%20a%20team%20of%20lawyers%2C%20art%20dealers%20and%20curators%20who%20ensure%20that%20only%20works%20officially%20associated%20with%20the%20Banksy%20brand%20get%20the%20certified%20Banksy%20seal%20of%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20is%20secret%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20been%20publicised%20because%20being%20a%20litigious%20art%20collective%20equally%20as%20dedicated%20to%20producing%20art%20as%20engaging%20in%20brand%20maintenance%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20evoke%20the%20solo%2C%20clandestine%2C%20provocative%20raconteur%20image%20Banksy%20is%20going%20for.%20Having%20a%20team%20of%20lawyers%20making%20sure%20only%20real%20Banksys%20are%20labelled%20as%20such%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20do%20much%20for%20your%20street%20cred.%20Still%2C%20revealing%20this%20publicly%20likely%20won%E2%80%99t%20diminish%20interest%20in%20Banksy%20or%20affect%20the%20price%20people%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20monkey%20stencils%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fartanddesign%2F2021%2Foct%2F14%2Fbanksy-auction-record-shredded-painting-love-is-in-the-bin%5C%22%3Eself-destroying%20art%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Ftyson-mitman-727091%5C%22%3ETyson%20Mitman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Senior%20Lecturer%20in%20Sociology%20and%20Criminology%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Fyork-st-john-university-833%5C%22%3EYork%20St%20John%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversatio