0involves%20hours%20of%20laborious%20stirring%20of%20the%20milk%20rendering%20a%20thick%20pudding-like%20consistency%20dessert%2C%20which%20is%20then%20packed%20and%20sold%20to%20shops%20across%20the%20city.%20Kanak%20herself%20is%20able%20to%20produce%2016%20kg%20of%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fact%20she%20declares%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20she%20is%20paid%20Rs%2012%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20which%20she%20channels%20into%20the%20home%20expenses%20and%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20school%20fees.%20She%20credits%20Avijit%20Patra%20with%20turning%20her%20destiny%20around.%20The%2028-year-old%20has%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20Maa%20Kali%20Rabri%20Bhandar%20since%202020%2C%20prior%20to%20which%20his%20father%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331406%2Fwrestler-parmanand-jain-started-mahaveer-rabri-bhandar-became-iconic-eatery-of-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espearheading%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20multiple%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20units%20spread%20across%20the%20villages%20of%20Hooghly%20seem%20to%20function%20almost%20like%20clockwork%20to%20produce%20tons%20of%20sweet%20delight%20every%20day.%20It%20is%20almost%20like%20a%20movement%20that%20has%20been%20perfected%20over%20the%20years%20to%20fulfil%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20history%20and%20Avjit%20differ%20slightly%20in%20their%20theories%20on%20the%20origin%20of%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20former%20believes%20it%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20migration%20of%20Bengalis%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20while%20the%20latter%20credits%20a%20gentleman%20Pannalal%20Balti%20for%20the%20ingenious%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCYzLfOgFHRe%2F%3Fu